funGUI

Class ChoiceList

  • java.lang.Object
    • funGUI.List
      • funGUI.OptionList
        • funGUI.ChoiceList

  • public class ChoiceList
extends OptionList
    The ChoiceList inherits from the OptionList class. Instead of making up a list of options, only one of which can be chose, the ChoiceList makes a list of check boxes, each of which can be checked or left unchecked.
    Author:
    audrey
